          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "Self-supporting natural lithium foils, with",
                " thicknesses in the range 0.2 to 5 mg/cm2."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "DETECTOR": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "SIBAR"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " Surface-barrier  detectors  mounted  in   the",
                " focal  plane of a magnetic spectrometer were used to",
                " detect  recoiling  6He  and  6Li  nuclei  from   the",
                " (gamma,p0) and (gamma,n0+n1) reactions."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "COMMENT": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "Cross sections for  the  reactions  Li-7(gamma,n0+n2)",
                " and  Li-7(gamma,p0)  have  been  measured for photon",
                " energies in the range 60-120 MeV. Comparison is made",
                " between  the  data  and simple calculations based on",
                " the modified quasideuteron  and  quasifree  knockout",
                " models, which suggests that the former dominates."
              ]
            }
          ],
